i Handley, 1960, distributed from Honduras to trans-Andean South America, previously considered a subspecies of C. trinitatum.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Garbino, Guilherme S. T.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Lim, Burton K.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Tavares, Val\u00e9ria Da C.", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/7aaa1042b396745c0a2a5396acd6cd3d", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/8f373e48e1dc35e81a5c452a164f6c34f3be6c251fdec94543a19cabcef7aed0", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/AXT8YKAJ", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/AXT8YKAJ", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/e254dc54e2a319c32c151a1773fe1fda!/b113572-116133", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "1", "title": "Zootaxa", "volume": "4846"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/7aaa1042b396745c0a2a5396acd6cd3d"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:AXT8YKAJ"}, {"identifier": "10.11646/zootaxa.4846.1.1"}], "communities": [{"id": "batlit"}, {"id": "biosyslit"}], "relations": {"version": [{"index": 0, "is_last": true, "parent": {"pid_type": "recid", "pid_value": "13417419"}}]}}, "title": "Systematics of big-eyed bat